WEBVTT

08:06.859 --> 08:08.525
"Are you scared? Come to me!"

08:09.900 --> 08:11.817
"Plead! Beg! Cry before me"

08:13.150 --> 08:15.317
"Come on! Let's rip
them to pieces"

08:16.400 --> 08:18.234
"Cut them in half"

08:18.275 --> 08:21.275
"Fresh blood is all I want
to see all around me"

08:21.525 --> 08:24.775
"And it should make me high
in numerous ways"

08:24.859 --> 08:28.275
"Let me quench my thirst"
-Sir, please let go of me.

08:28.650 --> 08:31.525
"Let me kill you again"
